                CONVERT(DATE_FORMAT(tanggal, "%d-%m-%Y"), CHAR(20)) AS tanggal,
                kandang.nama_kandang,
                get_stock_ceker.net_qty AS current_stock,
                supplier.nama_supplier
                FROM 
                    do_masuk                 
                INNER JOIN kandang
                ON do_masuk.kandang_id = kandang.kandang_id
                INNER JOIN get_stock_ceker

                INNER JOIN supplier
                ON do_masuk.supplier_id = supplier.supplier_id
                WHERE
